Reed,

Thank you for your response to this feedback survey, we very much
appreciate it. I see you have configured two Custom Pre-merge Checks within
the organization, one for CODE QUALITY and the other for SPEC COMPLIANCE. I
understand the intent behind why you created both the checks. I'm curious
to hear, have you tried using Path-based Instructions
<https://docs.coderabbit.ai/guides/review-instructions> and/or Coding
Guidelines to ensure that CodeRababit's review refers to your specific code
quality requirements?

Additionally, our built-in checks for Issue Assessment
<https://docs.coderabbit.ai/pr-reviews/pre-merge-checks> should be able to
satisfy your spec compliance requirements. Did you try this and that didn't
satisfy your requirements? If so, could you elaborate please?

Best,
Sahana

